reviewText: I was in Egypt a few years ago. I passed up a chance to go to the Pyramids to go to a Cemetery here. I do not regret my decision.
This is one of those movies which takes its title from a famous battle, but deals with a group of characters in a tank several miles away.
Waste O'money. Same tank as in Sahara with Humphrey Bogart, similar story line (same Well I think) only poor film quality. And I'm a former Tanker. I love tanks, but this just didn't do it for me.
